 />\n有做開gym 但好耐都改善唔到 <br />\n個肚腩仲好凸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e614437de631aae5e7104cae4fb0107c2f69da31","tid":612061,"uid":6721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T09:23:58.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搵教練修正緊"},{"pid":"ef03cf2bfbe6517e54a907f318e4b2dc60664184","tid":612061,"uid":23485,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T09:39:11.000Z","msg":"其實要改善骨盆前傾，最好就係做一啲pilates動作。<br />\n練腹肌係有用，但係好多練腹肌嘅動作係要你控制到骨盆先可以做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即係你連自己骨盆前/後傾都控制唔到嘅時候，你根本就鎖唔實個腹肌，腹肌都發唔到力，咁仲練乜春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n增加骨盆嘅mobility 、伸展股四頭肌/髂腰肌/內收肌群/臀大中小肌/梨狀肌等等⋯缺一不可。<br />\nPelvic mobility exercise 悶係悶啲，但每日做5分鐘，幾個星期之內骨盆前傾就會改善。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5FSgdibCcsw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5FSgdibCcsw&d=icx43JrqEyES0dg6tHeT1L%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=d5a188d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/5FSgdibCcsw</a>"},{"pid":"f16984459fb2ca15c0ade7b2322b458db1cb92d6","tid":612061,"uid":17838,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"905d690e8aed7ed9b0e1355755f46db3ff24a792","tid":612061,"uid":38521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T09:13:04.000Z","msg":"有無咩改善到前傾既動作推薦<br />\n有做開gym 但好耐都改善唔到 <br />\n個肚腩仲好凸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T11:20:59.000Z","msg":"有無按鬆返啲腹部肌肉?<br />\n加上要再加強返啲核心肌群 可以做返啲 Plank<br />\n拉筋方面哩個動作非常唔錯<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.kknews.cc/SIG=18ands/1s8q0000q98q0p14nn1n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D18ands%2F1s8q0000q98q0p14nn1n.jpg&h=d5fa0c89&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c64e